items.name: Anime 3D Converter LoRA
items.description:
<lora:anime3d:1> will convert your anime model to a 3D style and bring new life to all of your old checkpoints. For some models it will change the style to a PVC figurine, for others it will make a pleasing artistic render with depth. This LoRA produces wildly different results depending on the model you use, so experiment!

Model used in sample image is OrangeMixs

Notes:

This LoRA can also be used as a heuristic tool. If the base model has photography blended in, it will produce more photo real results, if it has PVC models blended in those will show up, if it used 3D renders that will come out as well.

The effect should be largely agnostic, so it should respond to the underlying model style instead of applying a common one across base models.

If you combine this LoRA with your model and release a 2.5D or 3D version, I kindly ask that you link back to this page (you don’t have to though!)

items.name: 【Character】Hindenburg (Azur Lane)
items.description:
2023/7/19 update

Update dataset and training strategy.

Introduction

A LoRA model of Hindenburg from Azur Lane. The trigger tag is hindenburg \(azur lane\). The key features are red hair, demon girl, demon horns, ahoge, underboob, elbow gloves, pointy ears. 0.6 ~ 0.8 weights are good. The preview images are generated using 1.6 version, 2.0 version Yesmix and MeinaMix to verify the compatibility of this LoRA model on different base models.

This model still requires more images to improve its generalization ability.

Cautions (Must Read)

For anime model,

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

  • Some preview images are generated using 'Hires Fix' and upscaled using 'SD Upscale'. Thus, if you wanna generate the preview images, pls download the original preview images and analyze them using 'PNG INFO' in webui to get all generating information.

BTW, make sure set this option in 'Stable Diffusion' settings to 'CPU' to successfully regenerate the preview images with the same seed.

  • The training resolution of this model is 1024x1024, so generating resolution must not exceed this range. Try to use 'hires fix' to prevent this problem and help to generate higher-resolution images.

  • For 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) users, make sure add '--no-half-vae' in command line of webui to prevent generating black images. See voldy's log for the details of edit method. For high-performance GPU, make sure 'medvram' and 'lowvram' mode are disabled.

The BGM-71 TOW ("Tube-launched, Optically tracked, Wire-guided", pronounced /ˈtoʊ/) is an American anti-tank missile. TOW replaced much smaller missiles like the SS.10 and ENTAC, offering roughly twice the effective range, a more powerful warhead, and a greatly improved semi-automatic command to line of sight (SACLOS) that could also be equipped with infrared cameras for night time use.

First produced in 1970, TOW is one of the most widely used anti-tank guided missiles. It can be found in a wide variety of manually carried and vehicle-mounted forms, as well as widespread use on helicopters. Originally designed by Hughes Aircraft in the 1960s, the weapon is currently produced by Raytheon.

items.name: OLD_oneitemV1
items.description:
这次的Lora模型是训练生成任意白色背景的单体物体，包含人物、动物、工业产品、电子产品、家具、玩具模型等，目的是能够根据需求利用该Lora能更加稳定的生成纯白背景的物体图片，方便我们进行后期处理。初期测试，该lora模型特别适配lyriel系列大模型，其他2.5d和3d风格base模型可能要增加相匹配的Prompt和调整图片尺寸。

目前对一些2d基础大模型适配情况一般，这个可能是由于我训练的素材基本都是真实的3d物体图片。后期可增加对应的2d风格的图片进行优化训练，希望大家可以尝试用一下此Lora，如果能提出您的建议和实验结果可以分享出来，我这边进行改进，谢谢！


This LoRA model has been trained to generate individual objects with a pure white background, including people, animals, industrial products, electronic devices, furniture, toy models, and more. Its purpose is to provide a stable generation of object images with a white background, facilitating post-processing tasks according to specific requirements. In initial testing, this LoRA model has shown particularly good compatibility with the Lyriel series of large models. However, for other 2.5D and 3D style base models, it may be necessary to adjust the matching prompts and image sizes accordingly.

Currently, the adaptation of certain 2D base models is average, possibly due to the fact that the training dataset primarily consisted of real 3D object images. To improve this, I plan to include optimized training using 2D style images in the future. I encourage you to try out this LoRA model, and if you have any suggestions or experimental results to share, I would be grateful to receive them for further improvement. Thank you!

items.name: Big Daddy | BioShock
items.description:
Character Lora of Big Daddy with Little Sister cameo's from BioShock

Who dares harvest the little sisters ? -soul3142

Can produce BS1 Bouncer and BS2 Alpha variant (rng and prompt dependent).


This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International License.

If you want to, you can support me on Patreon or Buy me Coffee.

Main Trigger Word - bigdaddyBS_soul3142 , check examples for other ones.

RECOMMENDATIONS :-

  1. Highres Fix - must, if you are getting blurry and ugly images

    My upscale method: txt2img 512x768 -> send to img2img -> controlnet tile upscale, tile diffusion 2x scale with 4xUltrasharp upscaler and tiled vae

  2. Weight: 0.6 - 0.8

  3. Clip Skip: 2

  4. Denoising - Don't go too high, it can alter a lot of details

  5. For better face's - you can use ADetailer

I use 0.7 weight, 25 steps, Euler a, Clip skip 2 in nearly all my examples with almost same, simple +ve/-ve prompts regardless of checkpoint for my own consistency purposes.

There are imperfections here & there, which i usually leave it in as is, (i never do any inpainting in examples), most of which like hands can be fixed with better prompting, negative embeddings while other like weapons are just bad majority of the time no matter the model as of today.

Some LoRA's are flexible with any clothing, some are not (usually character's with single costume) so keep these things in mind.

This is an unofficial fanmade LoRA, not intended for any commercial purpose and use. All characters and IP rights are owned by their respective creators and owners. I do not own rights to any of these characters.

items.description:

  • a photo of vineeta8, a woman [rest of the prompt]

Helpful Tips:

  1. Use ADetailer for full body shots. It may also sometimes help in medium shots but it is optional.

  2. Include this in the main negative prompt: makeup, shiny face, oily face

  3. Try to avoid using both ADetailer and Hi-Res fix for closeups and medium body shots. Do whatever you want in full body shots.

  4. Portrait dimensions like 512x768 yielded better results in my testing.

items.name: DunhuangMix 敦煌 飞天 古风
items.description:
敦煌大模型，使用了大批量的敦煌素材进行训练，并且多次筛选融合而来。

大模型与敦煌lora有什么区别：

1.模型的训练集合更大，更高清，细节还原更好

2.更趋向与真实的质感和光影，dunhuangV3版本为了兼容动漫和真实模型，更偏向于2.8D，衣物流线型更飘逸，各有取舍

3.对真实场景的泛化性更强

4.出图稳定性增强，简单提示加抽卡，可以获得高质量作品，上手门槛更低

5.肢体和脸更稳定

以下为推荐参数：

vae：840000

采样：DPM++ 2M SDE Karras

步数：20-30

高分辨率修复 (Hires. fix)：高清修复一定要开！！！

高清迭代步数:15-20

放大算法：8x_NMKD-Superscale_150000_G或者R-ESRGAN 4x+

重绘幅度：0.25-0.4

放大倍数：2或者2以上

cfg：7（可自由尝试）

特别鸣谢：墨幽、Majic，融合的大模型中包含MajicV6，墨幽完整版V1010

Dunhuang large model, using a large number of Dunhuang materials for training, and several screening fusion.

The following are recommended parameters:

Sample: DPM++ 2M SDE Karras

Hires: HD fix must be on!!

Added CleavageHelper-Anime. Use that for anime, and the regular version for non anime. Both will work to an extent on either, but the regular was was trained, tuned, and tested for good results on non-anime models, and the Anime version was trained, tuned, and tested for good results on anime models instead.

Regular description follows.

The purpose of this Lycoris is to help attain the best type of cleavage. You'll get the good results if you have the word "cleavage" in your prompt. items.name: Pullup LORA v1.0 - Realistic ABDL
items.description:
A LORA for making pretty ladies wearing pullup diapers.

If you like my work you can tip me through Comiss.io.

When I wanted to make SD pictures of ABDL stuff I quickly got frustrated that there weren't a lot of resources, so I decided to start making my own. This is the first release, and it covers pullup diapers.

Polite notice: This LORA only depicts adults doing consensual adult things, and fully complies with the TOS at CivitAI.

The trigger is just pullup and I suggest strength 0.8 for your starting point. The previews were all generated with fairly simply prompts and no other resources but I do use ADetailer, so you may not be able to perfectly recreate them.

The training set was around 100 images and I tried to cover all well known pullups but I haven't tried to teach it about brands, so prompt for colours and patterns if you specifically want them. The default pullup is pretty neutral, but leans towards purple/lilac.

This LORA is fairly transparent, and reacts reasonably well to other LORAs. It works quite well with controlnets, but you will have to adjust if you are using depth or lineart maps that show non-pullup undies.

It's presently trained on lazymixRealAmateur but I'm open to re-running it for other models if there is a demand for them. The LORA does somewhat work on other popular models, but it's less consistent and you'll need to dial in your own strength and CFG to get it to look good.

This is the first release version of the first thing I've made for SD, so expect some quirks! You can see the journey I've had putting this together on my creator profile, but I am actually pretty excited to have something I feel is good enough to post up.

On the list for next version:

  • Wetting and wet pullups
